1. Data we collect

Exotic Car DeX may collect and store the following information:

Discord user IDs
Discord server (guild) IDs
Basic gameplay data (such as car collections, catches, and progress)
Command usage required for bot functionality

We do not collect sensitive personal information such as passwords, email addresses, or payment details.

2. How we use data

The collected data is used only to:

Run core bot features (car spawning, catching system)
Track user progress and collections
Maintain leaderboards and competition systems
Improve gameplay balance and features
3. Data storage

Some bot data (such as user collections and server settings) may be stored to ensure the bot functions properly across restarts.

We do not sell, share, or distribute user data to third parties.

4. Message content

Exotic Car DeX may process message content only when required for gameplay features (for example, when a user types a car name to catch a spawned car).

Message content is not stored or logged permanently and is only used for immediate gameplay validation.

5. User control

Users can stop interacting with the bot at any time by removing it from their server or leaving the server where it is used.

Server administrators can remove bot data by removing the bot from the server.

6. Data sharing

We do not share, sell, or transfer user data to any third parties.

7. Changes

This Privacy Policy may be updated occasionally. Continued use of the bot means you accept the updated policy.

8. Contact

If you have any questions or concerns, you can contact the bot developer through the official support server.
